description: The extraordinary opportunity of owning in 584 East Third Street doesn't come around often.  Timelessly designed and impeccably built this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom third floor condominium with 2 garage parking defines South Boston Living.  Featuring expansive living space that showcases breathtaking windows, an abundance of natural light and ample space for and oversized dining room table.  The immaculate kitchen features custom cabinetry, Thermador appliances and gleaming quartz counters complete with a waterfall edge.  Offering a stunning primary suite complete with a custom California Closet walk-in.  Designer bathrooms features Porcelanosa tile, designer plumbing fixtures and Restoration Hardware lighting.  Full sized washer / dryer in unit, TWO direct-access garage parking spaces, surround sound speakers, professionally managed condo association and blocks from everything South Boston has to offer!
